WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:41.870 --> 00:01:46.460
Okobore Town

3
00:01:51.750 --> 00:01:54.260
Oh, are you awake?!

4
00:01:56.970 --> 00:01:59.710
Big Bro! Ma'am!

5
00:01:59.710 --> 00:02:01.340
Where am I?

6
00:02:02.260 --> 00:02:03.890
My teahouse.

7
00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:07.070
Otama!

8
00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.910
How's your tummy?

9
00:02:13.060 --> 00:02:14.940
Does it hurt?

10
00:02:22.390 --> 00:02:25.700
I feel better!

11
00:02:27.500 --> 00:02:29.330
That worked so fast!

12
00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:33.670
Five finger grass is quite the wonder drug.

13
00:02:33.670 --> 00:02:36.580
Thank you all!

14
00:02:37.470 --> 00:02:40.320
Nin-nin!

15
00:02:40.320 --> 00:02:41.010
But...

16
00:02:43.240 --> 00:02:46.470
the poison in your body
can't be removed completely.

17
00:02:46.470 --> 00:02:51.730
So don't ever drink
the river water again, Otama.

18
00:02:51.730 --> 00:02:53.980
Okay, I got it!

19
00:02:58.150 --> 00:03:01.570
Stop making noise, stomach!
This is unbecoming of a warrior!

20
00:03:01.570 --> 00:03:03.450
Water!

21
00:03:03.450 --> 00:03:05.950
River!

22
00:03:05.950 --> 00:03:09.290
Otama! Stop right there!

23
00:03:15.710 --> 00:03:17.550
You must never...!

24
00:03:17.550 --> 00:03:18.920
Huh?

25
00:03:18.920 --> 00:03:20.050
What?!

26
00:03:20.050 --> 00:03:22.090
You must never...

27
00:03:22.090 --> 00:03:24.970
drink the river water again!

28
00:03:27.140 --> 00:03:31.690
There, all done. This is only
a field dressing though...

29
00:03:31.690 --> 00:03:33.980
Yeah. Thank you.

30
00:03:36.460 --> 00:03:38.780
You're so huge.

31
00:03:40.700 --> 00:03:44.200
Big Mom was way bigger.

32
00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:51.080
Thank you for saving me from
the sumo wrestler's attempt at courtship.

33
00:03:53.590 --> 00:03:55.670
I didn't do anything.

34
00:03:57.630 --> 00:04:00.400
I forgot to introduce myself.

35
00:04:00.400 --> 00:04:04.680
I am your humble servant, Okiku.

36
00:04:05.230 --> 00:04:06.260
Humble servant?!

37
00:04:09.500 --> 00:04:10.640
What?!

38
00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:14.980
I can't! No way! I can't!

39
00:04:21.530 --> 00:04:24.950
Please! Take it away, ma'am!

40
00:04:28.790 --> 00:04:32.250
I don't even have money for the herbs!

41
00:04:32.250 --> 00:04:35.370
I can't possibly afford your
oshiruko red-bean soup!

42
00:04:41.710 --> 00:04:44.010
You don't have to pay for it.

43
00:04:45.100 --> 00:04:45.760
No!

44
00:04:46.490 --> 00:04:47.680
I can't have it!

45
00:04:50.810 --> 00:04:55.520
I know both you and Okiku
haven't had much to eat either!

46
00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:57.900
That's okay. Don't be shy.

47
00:04:58.640 --> 00:05:02.940
You've already saved my life
and now you're trying to give me food!

48
00:05:02.940 --> 00:05:05.740
How can I accept this?!

49
00:05:05.740 --> 00:05:06.990
It's okay.

50
00:05:06.990 --> 00:05:08.160
No!

51
00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:09.330
I said it's okay!

52
00:05:09.330 --> 00:05:12.620
I'll pay you back for the herbs
no matter what!

53
00:05:19.570 --> 00:05:22.550
That's enough!

54
00:05:22.550 --> 00:05:23.510
What?!

55
00:05:23.510 --> 00:05:26.220
When a woman has served food...

56
00:05:26.760 --> 00:05:27.840
"I don't want it."

57
00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:28.970
"Okay."

58
00:05:29.430 --> 00:05:33.140
Do you honestly believe
she'll just take it back?

59
00:05:35.250 --> 00:05:37.350
If you're not gonna eat it...

60
00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:41.570
I'll pour it in the street!

61
00:05:43.070 --> 00:05:45.100
No!

62
00:05:45.590 --> 00:05:47.240
Otama, just eat it!

63
00:05:47.240 --> 00:05:50.700
Miss Otsuru won't take no for an answer.

64
00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:03.800
How long are you gonna sit like that?

65
00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:08.890
You should be happy! Today's your birthday!

66
00:06:08.890 --> 00:06:10.680
Is that true?

67
00:06:11.230 --> 00:06:12.640
That's what I heard.

68
00:06:12.640 --> 00:06:16.570
Then, consider it a birthday gift...

69
00:06:17.030 --> 00:06:18.350
and eat up.

70
00:07:08.820 --> 00:07:12.070
It's so yummy!

71
00:07:13.820 --> 00:07:17.540
This soup is so delicious!

72
00:07:18.830 --> 00:07:19.690
What?

73
00:07:20.450 --> 00:07:23.540
Is this your first time having it?!

74
00:07:23.540 --> 00:07:24.590
Yes!

75
00:07:27.340 --> 00:07:32.090
How many days do you think it's been
since she last ate anything?!

76
00:07:32.090 --> 00:07:37.380
Despite how hard she works everyday to weave and sell hats,

77
00:07:37.380 --> 00:07:41.480
there is barely enough money
to sustain even a single person!

78
00:07:50.950 --> 00:07:53.670
There's even mochi in it!

79
00:07:54.380 --> 00:07:56.950
What a fancy treat!

80
00:08:00.090 --> 00:08:02.210
Can't you make some out of your cheek?

81
00:08:04.510 --> 00:08:07.290
You can't fill your stomach with those.

82
00:08:07.290 --> 00:08:10.260
Yum-yum!

83
00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:16.430
Ma'am! Thank you very much!

84
00:08:18.850 --> 00:08:23.310
I don't think I could ever top
such a wonderful birthday!

85
00:08:24.180 --> 00:08:26.870
I feel bad that my master is missing out!

86
00:08:33.800 --> 00:08:34.990
Otsuru...

87
00:08:43.580 --> 00:08:47.700
This is the greatest day of my life!

88
00:09:06.810 --> 00:09:09.610
Children like her are not uncommon...

89
00:09:10.670 --> 00:09:12.880
here in Wano...

90
00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:17.450
It's unbelievable that a small child
like her doesn't have enough to eat!

91
00:09:17.450 --> 00:09:21.600
At least when you're grown up,
you can handle the poison.

92
00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:22.580
No, you can't!

93
00:09:23.160 --> 00:09:28.960
There's the sea, the mountains, and the forests,
so getting food shouldn't be a problem.

94
00:09:29.930 --> 00:09:31.090
True.

95
00:09:31.710 --> 00:09:34.880
If we only we hadn't ruined them ourselves.

96
00:09:38.970 --> 00:09:40.640
Damn that Kaido!

97
00:09:41.680 --> 00:09:42.970
Yeah...

98
00:09:46.190 --> 00:09:48.480
You're such sweet young men.

99
00:09:49.350 --> 00:09:52.070
Oh, yeah! What are your names?

100
00:09:53.560 --> 00:09:56.170
My name is Zorojuro.

101
00:09:56.170 --> 00:09:57.490
I'm a ronin.

102
00:09:58.400 --> 00:09:59.870
I'm Monkey D.–

103
00:10:12.780 --> 00:10:14.430
His name is...

104
00:10:17.330 --> 00:10:18.430
Luffytaro.

105
00:10:18.430 --> 00:10:19.610
What?!

106
00:10:20.300 --> 00:10:22.430
R-Right...

107
00:10:24.550 --> 00:10:25.980
I'm Luffytaro...!

108
00:10:26.770 --> 00:10:27.900
Um...

109
00:10:27.900 --> 00:10:29.100
Verily...?

110
00:10:33.610 --> 00:10:35.110
You're outsiders, right?

111
00:10:36.190 --> 00:10:38.490
It must've been hard to enter the country.

112
00:10:38.490 --> 00:10:40.200
How could you tell?

113
00:10:40.200 --> 00:10:42.020
You speak strangely.

114
00:10:42.020 --> 00:10:42.990
– What?!
– What?!

115
00:10:42.990 --> 00:10:46.800
Don't worry. I won't tell anybody.

116
00:10:48.790 --> 00:10:51.810
I'm new to this town, too.

117
00:10:51.810 --> 00:10:56.340
And Okiku has only been
working here for a month.

118
00:10:57.340 --> 00:11:00.050
I heard this town is called Okobore.

119
00:11:00.050 --> 00:11:02.440
What kind of name is that?

120
00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:03.970
It speaks for itself.

121
00:11:05.010 --> 00:11:10.700
It means "leftovers," and we live off the scraps
of the officials the next town over.

122
00:11:11.250 --> 00:11:14.900
Tama said there is
non-poisonous food somewhere.

123
00:11:14.900 --> 00:11:17.030
Look over there.

124
00:11:19.020 --> 00:11:21.600
You see the mountain without chimneys?

125
00:11:22.180 --> 00:11:26.700
Once upon a time, Oden Castle stood atop it.

126
00:11:27.800 --> 00:11:30.920
It's already been twenty years.

127
00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:36.130
Oden... I've heard that
word before. But where?

128
00:11:37.130 --> 00:11:39.450
Until some twenty years ago...

129
00:11:40.120 --> 00:11:45.060
the Kozuki clan had long governed
the country of Wano.

130
00:11:48.110 --> 00:11:52.930
There is a vast farm at
the foot of that mountain...

131
00:11:52.930 --> 00:11:56.210
that was created by the late Lord Oden

132
00:11:56.210 --> 00:12:00.460
and fed the people of Kuri delicious food.

133
00:12:19.460 --> 00:12:26.390
It wasn't meant for Orochi and his cronies
to monopolize the country's food supplies.

134
00:12:29.490 --> 00:12:31.600
Halcyon Farm...

135
00:12:34.090 --> 00:12:35.520
I can hear you!

136
00:12:35.520 --> 00:12:39.570
So the food there isn't poisonous?

137
00:12:40.680 --> 00:12:41.820
Correct.

138
00:12:42.620 --> 00:12:47.030
There is safe, delicious food,
clean water, and clothes.

139
00:12:47.030 --> 00:12:49.370
However, it all belongs to...

140
00:12:49.370 --> 00:12:53.280
Shogun Orochi!

141
00:12:57.070 --> 00:13:01.050
On the other side of the shrine gate,
there is a town where the officials live.

142
00:13:01.690 --> 00:13:08.260
To survive, we beg them to sell us rotting food
and other things they no longer use.

143
00:13:10.290 --> 00:13:12.270
Okobore, the "leftovers" town...

144
00:13:12.270 --> 00:13:16.770
We get by. At least, we have enough to live.

145
00:14:04.310 --> 00:14:08.360
What do you think you're doing?!
Don't get in my way!

146
00:14:09.660 --> 00:14:12.770
I heard what you said, woman!

147
00:14:12.770 --> 00:14:15.620
You were bad-mouthing the shogun!

148
00:14:17.750 --> 00:14:21.500
I can hear six times better
than normal humans!

149
00:14:17.750 --> 00:14:23.250
Batman
Bat SMILE Fruit Gifter

150
00:14:21.500 --> 00:14:24.590
I won't miss a foul word spoken
about the Shogun!

151
00:14:28.270 --> 00:14:30.430
So you heard her.

152
00:14:30.430 --> 00:14:33.260
Was that really enough reason
to try and take her life?

153
00:14:34.040 --> 00:14:36.060
She would've died if you'd hit her.

154
00:14:38.280 --> 00:14:42.190
If you live quietly, I'll rarely need to hurt you!

155
00:14:43.220 --> 00:14:44.860
But Shogun Orochi...

156
00:14:44.860 --> 00:14:50.320
isn't one to let treasonous spirits live on!

157
00:15:24.980 --> 00:15:26.320
My arrows!

158
00:15:27.230 --> 00:15:29.740
He blocked all of them!

159
00:15:29.740 --> 00:15:32.010
Who are you?!

160
00:15:32.010 --> 00:15:36.030
Someone's been robbing
the farm for several weeks.

161
00:15:36.030 --> 00:15:40.250
We are currently on the lookout for culprits!

162
00:15:40.250 --> 00:15:43.420
Perhaps it was you two all along!

163
00:15:49.590 --> 00:15:51.840
A one-eyed ronin?!

164
00:15:54.220 --> 00:15:58.020
Zorojuro the Slasher

165
00:15:55.230 --> 00:15:58.020
I've seen him on a wanted poster!

166
00:16:14.160 --> 00:16:16.700
Let go of me!

167
00:16:17.580 --> 00:16:19.450
Who are you?!

168
00:16:20.220 --> 00:16:21.370
Otama!

169
00:16:22.960 --> 00:16:25.460
Help!

170
00:16:25.460 --> 00:16:28.420
Big Bro!

171
00:16:29.700 --> 00:16:30.590
Tama...

172
00:16:32.090 --> 00:16:34.470
Tama!

173
00:16:34.840 --> 00:16:38.760
Gazelleman
Gazelle SMILE Fruit Gifter

174
00:16:36.860 --> 00:16:39.060
Mission accomplished!

175
00:16:42.350 --> 00:16:45.020
Give Tama back!

176
00:16:58.740 --> 00:17:00.290
Okiku!

177
00:17:08.380 --> 00:17:09.880
A sword?!

178
00:17:11.970 --> 00:17:13.380
He runs so fast!

179
00:17:13.800 --> 00:17:15.880
Let go of me!

180
00:17:16.260 --> 00:17:18.640
Shut up, you little brat!

181
00:17:18.970 --> 00:17:21.350
I'm hopping on, sir lion-dog!

182
00:17:26.950 --> 00:17:27.840
Here, boy!

183
00:17:35.150 --> 00:17:37.950
That woman has a sword!

184
00:17:37.950 --> 00:17:39.910
She said she knew how to use it...

185
00:17:41.560 --> 00:17:43.750
Though I've never seen her in action...

186
00:17:46.710 --> 00:17:48.580
Heel, boy!

187
00:17:48.580 --> 00:17:50.840
Take me with you!

188
00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:55.420
Look at his arm!

189
00:17:57.630 --> 00:17:59.470
Wait!

190
00:17:59.470 --> 00:18:01.520
I'm coming too!

191
00:18:01.520 --> 00:18:02.310
Okay!

192
00:18:05.730 --> 00:18:07.930
Those mongrels!

193
00:18:11.490 --> 00:18:14.110
Luffytaro! Zorojuro!

194
00:18:17.040 --> 00:18:19.490
Why are they going after the kid?!

195
00:18:19.490 --> 00:18:23.120
I'm not sure, but we have to get her back!

196
00:18:25.370 --> 00:18:27.780
Tama!

197
00:18:27.780 --> 00:18:30.830
I'm gonna save you!

198
00:18:31.390 --> 00:18:33.750
Big Bro!

199
00:18:38.180 --> 00:18:41.010
Gazelleman! Run like the wind!

200
00:18:41.010 --> 00:18:43.310
Roger!

201
00:18:47.930 --> 00:18:50.400
How pathetic!

202
00:18:53.520 --> 00:18:55.130
Dammit!

203
00:18:55.130 --> 00:18:58.040
They must have planned this kidnapping!

204
00:18:58.040 --> 00:19:02.230
A headliner must've ordered it!

205
00:19:02.230 --> 00:19:05.660
There is only one place
to go in that direction...

206
00:19:07.670 --> 00:19:09.500
The town of officials.

207
00:19:11.790 --> 00:19:12.750
A notebook?

208
00:19:13.470 --> 00:19:16.260
There are three headliners in that town.

209
00:19:17.150 --> 00:19:18.360
Hawkins.

210
00:19:19.340 --> 00:19:20.390
Holdem.

211
00:19:21.570 --> 00:19:23.300
Speed.

212
00:19:23.300 --> 00:19:24.790
In addition...

213
00:19:25.140 --> 00:19:30.510
there are about thirty warriors with special
abilities from those strange artificial fruits.

214
00:19:32.730 --> 00:19:36.580
You're no ordinary woman.

215
00:19:38.770 --> 00:19:40.210
Who are you?

216
00:19:47.200 --> 00:19:48.660
This humble servant...

217
00:19:50.250 --> 00:19:51.530
is a samurai.

218
00:19:58.820 --> 00:20:02.090
Boss Holdem! This is Gazelleman!

219
00:20:02.660 --> 00:20:08.440
I caught the brat who
supposedly tamed our baboon!

220
00:20:09.560 --> 00:20:12.850
Let me go!

221
00:20:13.870 --> 00:20:16.280
Well done...

222
00:20:16.280 --> 00:20:18.820
We'll make good use of her.

223
00:20:19.380 --> 00:20:20.770
Bring her here.

224
00:20:20.770 --> 00:20:21.600
Yes, sir!

225
00:20:36.890 --> 00:20:40.670
Big Bro Luffy!

226
00:20:44.030 --> 00:20:49.120
This is Bakura, a prosperous town
in Wano's Kuri region.

227
00:20:57.110 --> 00:21:00.480
Restaurant

228
00:20:59.360 --> 00:21:00.480
Damn!

229
00:21:02.940 --> 00:21:05.320
That pesky ronin!

230
00:21:05.320 --> 00:21:08.860
I backed away due to his
strangely overpowering spirit,

231
00:21:08.860 --> 00:21:13.810
but I wanna take Okiku
as my wife at any cost!

232
00:21:15.080 --> 00:21:20.060
I have high social status, a good name,
and access to safe food supplies.

233
00:21:21.700 --> 00:21:24.630
She'd be crazy to reject me!

234
00:21:29.430 --> 00:21:33.310
Stop worrying over trifles, you idiot!

235
00:21:34.830 --> 00:21:37.320
She's a girl from Okobore Town, right?

236
00:21:37.320 --> 00:21:42.430
They're so low-class that Shogun Orochi
won't even rule over them...

237
00:21:45.740 --> 00:21:49.120
Whether she loves you or not
doesn't matter at all.

238
00:21:49.120 --> 00:21:52.610
You could just force the marriage...

239
00:21:52.610 --> 00:21:55.080
Or you could burn her house down...

240
00:21:55.900 --> 00:22:00.600
and kill all her relatives
so she'll have nowhere else to go.

241
00:22:01.150 --> 00:22:06.170
Isolate her and make her dependent on you!

242
00:22:09.300 --> 00:22:12.060
You're of the samurai class!

243
00:22:09.850 --> 00:22:16.770
Mouseman
Mouse SMILE Fruit Gifter

244
00:22:12.060 --> 00:22:16.770
In Wano, our status system is very clear.

245
00:22:21.770 --> 00:22:26.900
You're a star of our national sport, so if you
give a damn about a lowly person like that,

246
00:22:27.610 --> 00:22:30.760
you're not setting a good example for others!

247
00:22:33.740 --> 00:22:35.450
You're right!

248
00:22:36.910 --> 00:22:41.250
Yeah! I can do whatever I want with Okiku!

249
00:22:45.030 --> 00:22:48.630
Sir Yokozuna... Didn't you like the food?

250
00:22:52.970 --> 00:22:55.430
That's a tanuki, right?

251
00:22:55.430 --> 00:22:59.640
Yes, this is our long-time pet...

252
00:22:59.940 --> 00:23:02.050
Cook it!

253
00:23:02.050 --> 00:23:02.980
What?!

254
00:23:04.770 --> 00:23:07.440
Tanuki are my favorite food!

255
00:23:25.170 --> 00:23:30.010
Budo

256
00:23:34.450 --> 00:23:36.280
You're finally here...

257
00:23:51.240 --> 00:23:53.040
I see it!

258
00:23:57.540 --> 00:23:58.790
We'll charge right in!

259
00:23:58.790 --> 00:24:00.960
Luffytaro and Zorojuro!

260
00:24:01.830 --> 00:24:05.920
Beyond that point is Bakura Town!
The town of officials and pirates!

261
00:24:06.540 --> 00:24:08.630
I cannot guarantee our safety.

262
00:24:13.670 --> 00:24:15.890
Are you ready?!

263
00:24:17.230 --> 00:24:18.220
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

264
00:24:23.700 --> 00:24:25.290
Is this her?

265
00:24:28.040 --> 00:24:29.940
Poor girl...

266
00:24:30.690 --> 00:24:33.410
She's about to cry.

267
00:24:37.080 --> 00:24:39.510
I'm not gonna cry!

268
00:24:44.330 --> 00:24:46.490
Don't try to act tough!

269
00:24:44.870 --> 00:24:50.300
A Mansion
Bakura Town

270
00:24:59.100 --> 00:24:59.600
Ouch...

271
00:25:09.790 --> 00:25:12.030
There's a stitch in my side!

272
00:25:15.290 --> 00:25:18.070
Shut up! Gazelleman!

273
00:25:26.880 --> 00:25:31.520
You can go now!
Your heavy breathing annoys me!

274
00:25:38.680 --> 00:25:42.320
Build up your stamina, you idiot!

275
00:25:50.100 --> 00:25:52.730
I wasn't talking to you!

276
00:25:53.560 --> 00:25:58.240
Stop staring at me like that!

277
00:26:16.130 --> 00:26:19.030
I'm so scared!

278
00:26:16.260 --> 00:26:21.050
Holdem
Beast Pirates Headliner
Lion SMILE Fruit

279
00:26:19.540 --> 00:26:22.560
His tummy's a lion!

280
00:26:22.850 --> 00:26:27.020
Kamijiro
Holdem's Gut

281
00:26:28.390 --> 00:26:32.110
Oh? You're gonna give me that defiant look?

282
00:26:47.110 --> 00:26:48.580
What happened?

283
00:26:48.580 --> 00:26:52.170
There it is! The lion got him in the nuts!

284
00:26:57.160 --> 00:26:58.130
But...

285
00:26:58.130 --> 00:27:05.560
since they share the same body,
his groin also belongs to the lion!

286
00:27:10.400 --> 00:27:12.270
Why doesn't he learn?

287
00:27:12.270 --> 00:27:14.110
Boss Holdem.

288
00:27:14.110 --> 00:27:16.650
What should we do with this brat?

289
00:27:17.660 --> 00:27:18.950
Boss Holdem!

290
00:27:19.580 --> 00:27:21.450
So your name is Otama.

291
00:27:26.770 --> 00:27:32.330
How could a weak little shit like you...

292
00:27:34.120 --> 00:27:38.380
tame a savage baboon?!

293
00:27:38.380 --> 00:27:41.500
My men saw you do it!

294
00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:03.240
Don't pretend like you don't know!

295
00:28:03.240 --> 00:28:07.840
You must have a genuine devil fruit power.

296
00:28:11.190 --> 00:28:12.430
Come on...

297
00:28:13.170 --> 00:28:15.040
Spit it out!

298
00:28:18.060 --> 00:28:19.340
Otama!

299
00:28:19.340 --> 00:28:23.860
Your ability might be desirable to the enemy.

300
00:28:23.860 --> 00:28:27.560
You must never be seen using it!

301
00:28:39.440 --> 00:28:41.650
I-It's just...

302
00:28:43.450 --> 00:28:45.450
animals...

303
00:28:47.180 --> 00:28:50.540
tend to like me.

304
00:28:52.300 --> 00:28:54.450
Oh!

305
00:28:54.450 --> 00:28:56.080
I see!

306
00:28:56.080 --> 00:28:59.070
That's all it was!

307
00:29:01.520 --> 00:29:03.840
Yes, that's right.

308
00:29:05.470 --> 00:29:07.100
Do you think I'm a fool?!

309
00:29:09.680 --> 00:29:12.900
You damn brat!

310
00:29:16.500 --> 00:29:22.330
"She tore off part of her cheek."
That's what they told me.

311
00:29:35.910 --> 00:29:38.840
If you're not gonna tell me...

312
00:29:41.360 --> 00:29:43.720
I'll try that myself.

313
00:29:43.720 --> 00:29:45.970
Hey, bring me some pincers!

314
00:29:45.970 --> 00:29:47.220
Yes, sir!

315
00:29:51.430 --> 00:29:54.940
Not that one! The bigger one!

316
00:29:59.320 --> 00:30:02.570
Big Bro Luffy...

317
00:30:15.040 --> 00:30:20.630
Help! Big Bro Luffy!

318
00:30:22.750 --> 00:30:25.300
Tama!

319
00:30:30.450 --> 00:30:34.060
Stop right there! Don't you value your lives?!

320
00:30:34.060 --> 00:30:35.850
Invaders!

321
00:30:36.470 --> 00:30:38.690
Bakura Town is just past them!

322
00:30:38.690 --> 00:30:42.440
Luffy! We don't have time
to fight those weaklings!

323
00:30:43.810 --> 00:30:45.110
I know!

324
00:30:45.110 --> 00:30:47.570
Just keep charging, boy!

325
00:30:52.700 --> 00:30:54.830
What?!

326
00:30:55.430 --> 00:30:57.250
Captain!

327
00:30:58.440 --> 00:31:00.150
We have a problem!

328
00:31:04.270 --> 00:31:06.010
Captain!

329
00:31:06.010 --> 00:31:08.670
What? Why are you so worked up?

330
00:31:10.070 --> 00:31:12.430
It's Straw Hat and Roronoa!

331
00:31:13.860 --> 00:31:18.710
Straw Hat is in Wano?!
So... he's finally here...

332
00:31:18.710 --> 00:31:23.110
Straw Hat and Roronoa are
storming Bakura Town!

333
00:31:24.360 --> 00:31:28.600
Hey, wait! That's gonna cause
nothing but trouble!

334
00:31:28.600 --> 00:31:30.490
Pretty much...

335
00:31:32.200 --> 00:31:33.280
Captain?

336
00:31:35.970 --> 00:31:37.580
Captain?!

337
00:31:39.780 --> 00:31:42.130
Let's go stop those idiots!

338
00:31:42.870 --> 00:31:44.710
Aye aye, Captain!

339
00:31:53.260 --> 00:31:55.890
Don't do it...

340
00:31:57.910 --> 00:32:01.970
I'll stop as soon as you show me your ability.

341
00:32:22.030 --> 00:32:25.290
Tama!

342
00:32:41.330 --> 00:32:42.140
What?!

343
00:32:42.140 --> 00:32:43.980
Did you do something?!

344
00:32:46.370 --> 00:32:47.520
That was haki!

345
00:32:47.520 --> 00:32:48.590
Haki?

346
00:32:49.480 --> 00:32:51.240
Conqueror's haki.
